-- Jones Apparel near $825 mln Barneys sale: report
-- 
-- Fri Jun 22, 2007 1:45am EDT
-- http://www.reuters.com/article/2007/06/22/us-barneys-sale-idUSN2243322820070622

 

 NEW YORK  (Reuters) - Jones Apparel Group Inc. ( JNY.N ) is near a deal to sell the Barneys New York department store chain for $825 million to Dubai's private equity firm Istithmar, The New York Times reported on Friday. 

 A deal could be announced on Friday, the Times said, citing people involved in the talks. Jones Apparel did not immediately return a call seeking comment. A spokeswoman for Istithmar in Dubai could not immediately be reached.